Remember, aero is a very modular project
For example, aero can build the SW code inside (root/src), but in order for everything to work in production AeroSandbox must be built first (inside of root/src/AeroSandbox), and there are many subprojects like my JS (ProxyParse), XML, and HTML Rewriters.